  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dbd \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dca\u0da8\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dba\u0dda  \u0dc3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dc3\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Four commit suicide in Monaragala police division in a week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four residents of the Monaragala Police Division have committed suicide in the last one week on the 26th, according to Monaragala Hospital sources.",
        "A 17-year-old school student from Hindikiula, Monaragala, a 28-year-old married man from Dombagahawela, a 34-year-old married man from Buttala Bodhiyapara Pillawela and a 22-year-old mother of one from Kumbukkana Galwala Road in Moneragala have committed suicide.",
        "Investigations have revealed that these people have committed suicide due to various reasons including love affair breaks, family disputes and economic problems.",
        "The police said that suicide has become a social problem and that the public should be made aware of the fact that government officials and NGO activists working at the village level should be made aware of this."
      ],
